{"tid":239684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好絕對相信死因庭 其中都有唔少案係死因離奇最後不了了之","createTime":"2017-05-11T23:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T03:05:39.000Z","uid":3117,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2666d4b9644e176aec80b6c07e09c229486571","tid":239684,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3376928&amp;page=1&amp;pos=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D3376928%26page%3D1%26pos%3D0&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=069c770b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3376928&amp;page=1&amp;pos=0</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係高登既post 不過入邊就例舉左法醫官 警犬行為失當<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔少案件係好離奇 不過最後死因都係死因不明/死於自然 要知道警犬交俾死因庭既報告係會對案件好大影響 同埋警犬同埋傳媒已經講到個疑犯絕對係自殺咁 對第日陪審團既判決絕對係有影響<br />\n<br />\n同埋咁多年黎差唔多年年都有唔少疑犯係警署內死於非命 不過最後都係不了了之"},{"pid":"2c270cc7b3d232b49c273bce3f1e687c63b38c37","tid":239684,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9020671fa159fdbf76fb69872f75396cab80c0a","tid":239684,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:38:25.000Z","msg":"咁信邊個?<br />\n你認為法醫唔夠專業? 你覺得搜証有包庇?"},{"pid":"f79a2bb5561d3dd00fffee7034e4dc24f03fc054","tid":239684,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05990a3880b3503c4977ce970375590d52c225fb","tid":239684,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證據一經黑警手變左啲咩自己諗啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7a724ce9f3f28ce2428b6dfbc8819070c60baa","tid":239684,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:18:56.000Z","msg"