rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩人都唔好信，離開地球先"},{"pid":"92b5c759acf0ffebd864047e6d6e188403c7d132","tid":239684,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"383adde9c924e4d4cdcf8fd40ea49342c030ca96","tid":239684,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>證據一經黑警手變左啲咩自己諗啦</blockquote><br />\n咁講又太過份啦 黑警做同政治地產無關既野都唔會咁流既</blockquote><br />\n睇下高登個post 警署入面疑犯離奇死亡唔有唔少 仲話唔會流？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2014年1單自殺 咁大把</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年疑犯押返屋企自己跳樓死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個疑犯係咪有畏罪而自殺? 單案應該有結論啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結論咪阿sir 做野唔使你教。兩個黑警都阻佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天水圍天華邨今午發生男疑犯墮樓命案。據了解，死者為58歲姓陳男子，他涉及在麥當勞分店偷取銀包被捕，今午由約3名探員押返天華邨華萃樓17樓寓所搜查，其間突然推開窗戶躍出，墮地後當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息指，死者當時沒戴手銬，事發時2名探員企圖阻止他躍下，糾纏間受輕傷，事後需送院治理。案件現交由新界北總區重案組跟進，將調查死者因何墮樓，以及押解疑犯的程序是否需要改善。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者有盜竊案底，他涉嫌於本月18日在一間麥當勞內偷取顧客銀包，警方接報後，按相關人士的口供及閉路電視片段影像綜合調查，迅速鎖定疑犯身分，元朗特遣隊探員今日較早前將陳拘捕，詎料今午5時許將他押往天華邨華萃樓寓所搜查時，疑犯報稱要入房取物，卻突然推開窗戶，探員曾上前阻知，但疑犯身型魁梧及極力掙扎，最終躍出墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n大批警員封鎖現場調查，屍體由帳篷覆蓋，等候重案組探員及法醫到場。2名稱阻止疑犯跳樓時受傷的探員，事後需送院敷治，並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472222406632#sthash.6kk10x00.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160826%2Fs00001%2F1472222406632%23sthash.6kk10x00.dpuf&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c287be71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160826%2Fs00001%2F1472222406632%23sthash.6kk10x00.dpuf&h=cc094820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472222406632#sthash.6kk10x00.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"5651fa547428c89f4af0d533417fdfece97b9d87","tid":239684,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>綜合呢幾日神探分析，大家唔好信DNA，唔好信死因庭，唔 好信黑警，唔好信法官，唔好個證物，唔好信條女<br />\n<br />\n咁我信邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信連登神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以close file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續番工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你話警察拉個無關既人返黎屈佢 扮破案再整死佢死無對證<br />\n首先整死佢 班警察有咩著數先 影響升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次法醫點解要幫警察先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做任何野都要有得益有目的先得嫁<br />\n盲反到咁<br />\n樣樣都唔信得"},{"pid":"b1c2b92744f379f9288eb87f61393ef388b295c8","tid":239684,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>綜合呢幾日神探分析，大家唔好信DNA，唔好信死因庭，唔 好信黑警，唔好信法官，唔好個證物，唔好信條女<br />\n<br />\n咁我信邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信連登神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩人都唔好信，離開地球先</blockquote><br />\n咁其實討論落去都冇意思, 因為基本黑警, 法醫同法官都唔可信都前提下, 就算最後有判決都係唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"cf8645ea856d1f1c03744deb84fef7097546f24d","tid":23