oji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以close file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續番工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你話警察拉個無關既人返黎屈佢 扮破案再整死佢死無對證<br />\n首先整死佢 班警察有咩著數先 影響升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次法醫點解要幫警察先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做任何野都要有得益有目的先得嫁<br />\n盲反到咁<br />\n樣樣都唔信得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打犯一向有。打到佢認咪紮職。錯手打死有乜咁奇。<br />\n<br />\n有腦就唔係黑警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咁易升職就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家犯罪咁低。唔搏真係世散仔<br />\n<br />\n砌生豬肉衰已經有前科。"},{"pid":"45d826c49d2db752cde59210d7d3644d009daacf","tid":239684,"uid":7709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:51:43.000Z","msg":"唔信死因庭唔通信你，因為你睇得查案劇多呀？<br />\n死傻系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473c631e097061256a44159fcdc77001d7ad4dea","tid":239684,"uid":32221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:58:43.000Z","msg":"求其捉個人都講得出<br />\n條女當日就去報警，肯定第一時間驗傷，身上冇可能冇個犯啲dna，係咪條友一查就知，你做黑警明知有證據夠唔夠膽求其捉條友砌佢，定你話驗身/法醫會全部一條龍幫晒黑警，如果係既我建議你都係快啲離開香港，太危險"},{"pid":"ea8ed81eab79c19e4416cf0180d7a08e07d2ed84","tid":239684,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:02:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d0e2eb5c568f9b40226d094368ac5ea11e7cb5d8","tid":239684,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>綜合呢幾日神探分析，大家唔好信DNA，唔好信死因庭，唔 好信黑警，唔好信法官，唔好個證物，唔好信條女<br />\n<br />\n咁我信邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信連登神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩人都唔好信，離開地球先</blockquote><br />\n咁其實討論落去都冇意思, 因為基本黑警, 法醫同法官都唔可信都前提下, 就算最後有判決都係唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，所以昨日聽完佢偉論已經無理過件事同討論過<br />\n<br />\n剩係走左去回CCTVB單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cb5d515e6fdef56eb255139c8e5f5106d669cf","tid":239684,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:07:53.000Z","msg":"香港人盲返已去到一個頂點"},{"pid":"d8899febbc7a5adb43e05500cfa10d36d1651e3d","tid":239684,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:11:13.000Z","msg":"死因庭一向9判，上次徐步高死因庭由陳碧橋審<br />\n有幾可信自己諗下"},{"pid":"3c72e89a4ebcf5ed6045948e761393a5962ca536","tid":239684,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78e03112dcb14655a021d024dcdcca5a933ae661","tid":239684,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"黑警唔可信 法醫唔可信 法官唔可信 <br />\n真係可信只有..？"},{"pid":"4800a5b976e58f1da1040aacc0b17d6f07925259","tid":239684,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:17:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"971eda3a75dc74f64d3ff3823b0f1d653d3ed2bc","tid":239684,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑警唔可信 法醫唔可信 法官唔可信 <br />\n真係可信只有..？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<