e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:40:23.000Z","msg":"成鳩日話人5毛護警，我夠可以話你係　5毛有心推翻香港人對專業、對法庭既信任以破壞香港既國際地位令香港減少得到國際支援，增加對中國既依賴達致維穩效果。<br />\n<br />\n要屈人5毛好撚簡單架咋"},{"pid":"908f56ec038467455c9eec17106e3fbf78c6679a","tid":239684,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a420145a0768cdc17038f2b82703fc4fbb545173","tid":239684,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咩都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415588eb8d0db1bdbec55b769272b9dbcc722fe4","tid":239684,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"又一個反社會人格 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188d4aff08ed427d625bac1fd363b4d43e297593","tid":239684,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又一個反社會人格 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有唔少事例 點樣反社會人格？"}]}